GTA GameWorld Renderer README
=============================

author: Dennis Yolkin [dennisyolkin (=a.t=) gmail.com]

Articles about file formats that were used: http://gtamodding.ru/wiki

Here is GtaLight project that also can render GTA gameworld:
http://b66883.com/projects/gtalight/gtalight_20090416_23-10.zip
(this link was found here: 
http://irrlicht.sourceforge.net/phpBB2/viewtopic.php?t=30439&postdays=0&postorder=asc&start=75).

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

[Note] encoding in most of files is cp1251 (Windows-Cyrillic).


Directories structure:
----------------------
GTA World Renderer -- Visual Studio 2008 project folder
GTA World Renderer\app_working_dir -- Program working directory. Now it contains of only configuration xml file and its schema.